page.title: 10Industry
page.content: {Frederic Smart & Son Ltd}have a mill situated Centrally in{Whittlesford, next to the school. They clean & store agricultural produce from the U.K & abroad. They trade in grain, by buying it from another place & selling it.They deliver by lorry on the side of which is written the firms name. {Ciba-Geigy Agro-Chemicals}is situated by the{M11 junction.}It makes sprays for killing weeds & bugs. Some employees are strategically placed around the country in farming areas. They sell fertilizer to farmers and tell them the correct dosage.{Volvo BM {U.K. Ltd}have a large factory on the outskirts of{Duxford.}They also have other branches in Sweden, Norway, France and Spain. They make construction equipment which consist of Rigid dumptrucks, articulated dumpers, wheel loaders and excavators.
